Tiger Woods and his wife Lindsey Vonn attended the Par 3 Contest at the Augusta National Golf Club in Augusta, Georgia on Thursday . 
  The event is part of the Masters tournament and is where golfers invite their wives, girlfriends and children to caddie . 
  Vonn wore a spaghetti strap dress and Louis Vuitton bag for the event . 
  Condoleezza Rice was also in attendance at the tournament . 
 